# Agent Skills Location

Skills for this repo live under `skills/` as `SKILL.md` files. Enumerate them with a traversal that includes every nested directory even when search tools would normally skip ignored paths:

```bash
find skills -type f -name SKILL.md -print
```

Read the relevant `SKILL.md` when your task overlaps the skill's subject (e.g., `skills/profile-isaac-sim/SKILL.md` for performance work).
